title: Actor Michael Traynor Previews 'The Walking Dead' Season 6
text:
Actor Michael Traynor Previews 'The Walking Dead' Season 6 He promises "a whole lot of epicness." Ryan Buxton Senior Editor, HuffPost Live Posted: 10/09/2015 03:41 PM EDT 
"The Walking Dead" returns for its sixth season this Sunday, and HuffPost Live's " Spoiler Alert " got a preview on Friday from Michael Traynor, who plays Nicholas in AMC's zombie apocalypse drama. Watch as Traynor and a panel of TV fanatics talk about what's to come this season, then break down this week's episodes of "American Horror Story: Hotel," "Scandal," "How To Get Away With Murder" and "Quantico."
